query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 s t1 u1) NoMergeJoin(a1 q1 s t1 u1 tq1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from answer AS a1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.name IN ('extension-field',
'factoring',
'improper-integrals',
'lie-groups',
'networking',
'notation',
'partitioning',
'server')
inner join question AS q1
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id group by t1.name;
